{"snp5.7:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 5.7 ","snp5.7:0.2":"Upasivamanavapuccha ","snp5.7:1.1":"“Eko aham sakka mahantamogham, ","snp5.7:1.2":"(iccayasma upasivo) ","snp5.7:1.3":"Anissito no visahami taritum; ","snp5.7:1.4":"Arammanam bruhi samantacakkhu, ","snp5.7:1.5":"Yam nissito oghamimam tareyyam”. ","snp5.7:2.1":"“Akincannam pekkhamano satima, ","snp5.7:2.2":"(upasivati bhagava) ","snp5.7:2.3":"Natthiti nissaya tarassu ogham; ","snp5.7:2.4":"Kame pahaya virato kathahi, ","snp5.7:2.5":"Tanhakkhayam nattamahabhipassa”. ","snp5.7:3.1":"“Sabbesu kamesu yo vitarago, ","snp5.7:3.2":"(iccayasma upasivo) ","snp5.7:3.3":"Akincannam nissito hitva mannam; ","snp5.7:3.4":"Sannavimokkhe parame vimutto, ","snp5.7:3.5":"Titthe nu so tattha ananuyayi”. ","snp5.7:4.1":"“Sabbesu kamesu yo vitarago, ","snp5.7:4.2":"(upasivati bhagava) ","snp5.7:4.3":"Akincannam nissito hitva mannam; ","snp5.7:4.4":"Sannavimokkhe parame vimutto, ","snp5.7:4.5":"Tittheyya so tattha ananuyayi”. ","snp5.7:5.1":"“Titthe ce so tattha ananuyayi, ","snp5.7:5.2":"Pugampi vassanam samantacakkhu; ","snp5.7:5.3":"Tattheva so sitisiya vimutto, ","snp5.7:5.4":"Cavetha vinnanam tathavidhassa”. ","snp5.7:6.1":"“Acci yatha vatavegena khitta, ","snp5.7:6.2":"(upasivati bhagava) ","snp5.7:6.3":"Attham paleti na upeti sankham; ","snp5.7:6.4":"Evam muni namakaya vimutto, ","snp5.7:6.5":"Attham paleti na upeti sankham”. ","snp5.7:7.1":"“Atthangato so uda va so natthi, ","snp5.7:7.2":"Udahu ve sassatiya arogo; ","snp5.7:7.3":"Tam me muni sadhu viyakarohi, ","snp5.7:7.4":"Tatha hi te vidito esa dhammo”. ","snp5.7:8.1":"“Atthangatassa na pamanamatthi, ","snp5.7:8.2":"(upasivati bhagava) ","snp5.7:8.3":"Yena nam vajjum tam tassa natthi; ","snp5.7:8.4":"Sabbesu dhammesu samohatesu, ","snp5.7:8.5":"Samuhata vadapathapi sabbe”ti. ","snp5.7:8.6":"Upasivamanavapuccha chatthi. "}